snippet.title: Enter the Chronosphere 🌐 9 minutes of gameplay
snippet.description:
A turn based bullet hell roguelike
Play for free: https://rhys_vdw.itch.io/enter-the-chronosphere

Journey to the heart of the Chronosphere 🌐

A game by Ned Kirner and Rhys van der Waerden
Music produced by Shisvi (https://soundcloud.com/shisvi)
